title: The Steve Wilkos Show 04.24.08
description:
IS SHE A LIAR?

    Melissa hasn&#039;t let her ex boyfriend see their 6-year-old son in almost three weeks. She alleges he molested their son three years ago, and she suspects he is continuing to do it today. But everyone else, including the police and child protective services, believe Melissa could be making the whole thing up in an attempt to keep her son to herself. With such a serious matter, Steve demands the truth, and he&#039;s going to get it.
